data.description: Price Reduced to SELL!! Bring all offers....This house won't last long! This Full Brick Low Maintenance home is situated on a large level lot, well-placed on a quiet street. This is  a rare find in the desirable Lincolnton area. The spacious open floorplan is perfect for entertaining. The Living Room features a fireplace and opens to the spacious kitchen and breakfast area. The split bedroom floorplan offers three bedrooms and two baths. Primary suite features a huge garden tub and walk-in closet. You will love entertaining on the oversized deck that overlooks a vast wooded and flat lot. The two car garage is climate controlled and has cable hook ups. This is a great space to work and or hang out year round. A gorgeous backyard and large lot complete this beautiful home.
